flowchart LR
    Buyer[买家] --> Reserve[预定商品]
    Buyer --> Cancel[取消预定]
    Buyer --> Favorite[收藏/取消收藏]
    Buyer --> Chat[私信卖家]
    Buyer --> ReadNotice[查看系统通知]

    Seller[卖家] --> Cancel
    Seller --> Complete[确认交易完成]
    Seller --> Chat
    Seller --> ReadNotice

    Reserve --> Lock[锁定商品库存]
    Reserve --> NotifySeller[通知卖家]
    Complete --> NotifyBuyer[通知买家]
